Lab 7: Preregistration

Purpose

The purpose of today’s lab is to walk through how to create a pre-registration on the Open Science Framework. Rather than serve as a step-by-step tutorial, this page will mostly contain links to other resources on pre-registration and open science along with a few questions/prompts to guide our discussion.
